        Default constructor.
        Parameters:
        result - The AsrResult instance.
        audioSource - The input source of the audio. If null is passed in, then the audio source is set to AudioSource.Unknown.
        inputId - The input ID to associate with this result. This will be used when constructing the log file name.
        isLowConfidence - True if the ASR result is considered low confidence. If so, this will have an additional extension appended to its file name.
